  <h2 id="blankslate">Blankslate</h2>
  <p>Blankslates are for when there is a lack of content within a page or section. Use them as placeholders to tell users why something isnâ€™t there. Be sure to provide an action to add content as well.</p>
  <p>Ported from <a href="http://primercss.io">PrimerCSS</a></p>


  <h3>Basic example</h3>

  <div class="bs-example">
    <div class="blankslate">
      <h3>This is a blank slate</h3>
      <p>Use it to provide information when no dynamic content exists.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

{{#markdown}}
